verbose_text: Inclusion of the DGLalpha inhibitor tetrahdydrolipstatin (THL, 5 muM) in the intra-pipette solution prevented the enhancement of GABA B IPSCs by AM251 (AM251 = 140.7% +/- 12.3%, n = 5; AM251 + intra-THL = 104.9% +/- 7.7%, n = 6; unpaired t test, p < 0.05; XREF_FIG).
